<paragraph blockId="55.[818,1442,1288,1571]" pageId="55" pageNumber="56">
<emphasis box="[818,920,1288,1307]" italics="true" pageId="55" pageNumber="56">Cybertype.</emphasis>
Volumetric raw data (in DICOM format), 3D rotation video, still images of surface volume rendering, and 3D surface (in PLY format) of the physical 
<typeStatus box="[1168,1249,1347,1366]" pageId="55" pageNumber="56">holotype</typeStatus>
(CASENT0235469) in addition to stacked digital color images illustrating head in full-face view, profile and dorsal views of the body. The data are deposited at Dryad (Hita Garcia et al. 2019, http://doi.org/10.5061/ dryad.3qm4183) and can be freely accessed as virtual representation of the type. In addition to the cybertype data at Dryad, we also provide a freely accessible 3D surface model of the 
<typeStatus box="[1336,1417,1523,1542]" pageId="55" pageNumber="56">holotype</typeStatus>
at Sketchfab (Model 13).
</paragraph>
