Still images from shaded surface display volume renderings of 
<taxonomicName authority="Hita-Garcia &amp; Lieberman &amp; Audisio &amp; Liu &amp; Economo, 2019" authorityName="Hita-Garcia &amp; Lieberman &amp; Audisio &amp; Liu &amp; Economo" authorityYear="2019" box="[730,825,1782,1799]" class="Insecta" family="Formicidae" genus="Discothyrea" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="56" pageNumber="57" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="michelae" status="sp. n.">
