<collectingCountry box="[885,970,1856,1875]" name="Tanzania" pageId="57" pageNumber="58">Tanzania</collectingCountry>
, where it was collected from leaf litter in a primary montane forest at an elevation of 
<quantity box="[1128,1200,1886,1905]" metricMagnitude="3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.739" pageId="57" pageNumber="58" unit="m" value="1739.0">1739 m</quantity>
(
<figureCitation box="[1212,1286,1885,1905]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="5.[146,173,1283,1300]" captionTargetBox="[153,1435,148,1247]" captionTargetId="figure@5.[152,1435,147,1248]" captionTargetPageId="5" captionText="Fig. 4. Maps showing the known distribution ranges of Afrotropical Discothyrea species." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3542140" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3542140/files/figure.png" pageId="57" pageNumber="58">Fig. 4M</figureCitation>
